title: 🎱 "Keep your face to the sunshine and you cannot see a shadow." - Helen Keller
content:
Print the ASCII printable characters code page (0x20-0x7E), without any built-ins or functions that do it for you.

Characters to be printed:

!"#$%&'()*+,-./
0123456789:;<=>?
@ABCDEFGHIJKLMNO
PQRSTUVWXYZ[\]^_
`abcdefghijklmno
pqrstuvwxyz{|}~
